00:20:50.239 --> 00:20:59.199
I think Jacqueline and Emily Robinson's book on data science careers

00:20:59.359 --> 00:21:07.520
has a really good definition for both and the subtle differences between the both of them.

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:14.160
I think, and this is going to be wrong because I don't recall those definitions, but I think maybe

